    <p>4.3.1 You must return any goods in new condition with all packaging and materials within 7 days of purchase. We will refund the purchase price of the goods (minus the direct costs of returning the goods) within 30 days of the date of cancellation.</p>
    <h3 style="text-align:center;"><strong>4.4 Statutory compensation</strong></h3>
    <p>4.4.1 We will repair, replace or refund the price of any goods returned to us during the six-month statutory warranty period, provided they are deemed defective after our assessment. All returns must follow our returns procedure in section 5 below.</p>
    <h3 style="text-align:center;"><strong>4.5 Restocking and Assessment Fees</strong></h3>
    <p>4.5.1 Should any returned product under section 3 or 4 meet any of the conditions in section 3.4, if the product is not working correctly due to human error or if the product is simply working correctly and as expected we reserve the right to charge an assessment fee of R150 ex VAT and if necessary a restocking fee.</p>
    <p><strong> </strong></p>
    <p><strong> </strong></p>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;"><strong>5. Returns Procedure </strong></h2>
    <p></p>
    <p style="text-align:center;"><strong>5.1 Return of unwanted goods</strong></p>
    <p>5.1.1 If you wish to return any unwanted goods and you have met the above-mentioned conditions in clause you may do so at your own cost together with your proof of purchase or order reference number. We then reserve the right to inspect the goods. Once we have inspected the product and validated your return, we will credit your account with the purchase price of the product (or refund you if that is your preference) within the required 30 days.</p>
    <p></p>
    <p style="text-align:center;"><strong>5.2 Return of defective goods</strong></p>
    <p>5.2.1 If you wish to return a product under section 3.2 we will require you to log a formal returns request by sending an email to <a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection#1e6d6b6e6e716c6a5e7a77677b727b7d6a6c7170777d6d307d7130647f"><span class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="added8ddddc2dfd9edc9c4d4c8c1c8ced9dfc2c3c4cede83cec283d7cc">[email&#160;protected]</span></a> stating that you would like to return a product and in the case of a defective product evidence to substantiate your claim. You will then be provided with a <strong>Returns Form</strong> to fill in which must then be submitted back to us and thereafter a collection will be booked by us for the defective item.</p>
    <p>5.2.2 We then reserve the right to inspect all goods returned under section 3.2. Once we have inspected the product and validated your return, we will repair / replace the product (if such repair is possible / we have the same product in stock to use as a replacement) or credit your account with the purchase price of the product (or refund you if that is your preference).</p>
    <p>5.2.3 Should we find that the product returned is not indeed defective or falls under section 3.4 above or does not meet the requirements in section 3.2 we reserve the right to revoke your claim or charge you for all repair and freight costs or any missing parts associated with the return.</p>
    <p>5.2.4 Should you wish to return a product under section 3 at a brick and mortar store you will be required to fill out all required information in our <strong>Returns Form </strong>at the store front and one of our agents will aid you in submitting your claim to our support division where the above mentioned returns procedure will then be followed.</p>
    <p></p>
    <p><strong> </strong></p>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;"><strong>6. Local shipping policies and procedures</strong></h2>
    <p>6.1 Orders will be shipped within the day of receipt of payment and not later than 2 days and are subject to availability. Delivery time may vary depending on which area items are being delivered to, but typical delivery times are between 2 and 4 working days. Please note that overnight shipping is only possible on these before mentioned working days. We will do our best to deliver your items as timeously as possible but shall not be held liable for any losses or damages of any kind incurred due to late delivery. Items are well packaged and protected. We reserve the right to charge our customers per the pricing structure mentioned in our delivery terms as well as change the pricing structure as we please without warning or consent. Once your package has been sent you will receive an e-mail confirming postal details including tracking and delivery information.</p>
    <p> </p>
    <h2 style="text-align:center;"><strong>7. International shipping policies and procedures</strong></h2>
    <p>7.1 Please note that shipping fees for any international orders are subject to quotation. Contact us for relevant rates and shipping periods. All terms and conditions mentioned above are applicable. Please note that all customs clearance, duties and fees are to be furnished by the customer and we will not be held liable for any loss or damage incurred in any form resulting from this process. Full value and complete packing list will be accompanied with your order.</p>
